      "gold_preview": "SOI-GaAs structures of GaAs/Ca x Sr 1-x F 2 /GaAs were fabricated by MBE techniques. MESFETs formed in the upper single crystal GaAs layers show clear on-off characteristics and a transconductance of 7 mS at a gate length of 17 \u03bcm. The intrinsic transconductance gm 0 increases from 25 mS/mm to 60 mS/mm with increasing carrier concentration from 1\u00d710 17 cm -3 to 7.5\u00d710 17 cm -3 . The breakdown voltages of the SOI-GaAs diodes are two or four times higher than those fabricated on the GaAs substrate, reflecting the very thin active layer limited by the presence of Ca x Sr 1-x F 2 insulators.",
